what_levels check the levels of many things

####  Description 

this function is used internally to check what the levels are of the dataframe.

####  Usage 
<pre><code>

what_levels(x)
</code></pre>
#### Arguments 

x data.frame, usually

#### Value 

a list containing the levels of everything
